<head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/home.css" />
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light fixed-top"></nav>
  <!-- company name -->
  <div class="company-details">
    <!-- <h1>Hi <%= name %></h1> -->
    <form action="/logout?_method=DELETE" method="POST">
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-dark">Log Out <%= name %></button>
    </form>
  </div>
  

  <div
    id="carouselExampleIndicators"
    class="carousel slide"
    data-ride="carousel"
  >
    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
      <li
        data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators"
        data-slide-to="0"
        class="active"
      ></li>
      <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
      <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
    </ol>
    <div class="carousel-inner">
      <div class="carousel-item active">
        <img
          class="d-block w-100"
          src="img/home-1.jpg"
          alt="First slide"
        />
        <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
          <h5>What is CoalEx?</h5>
          <p>
            CoalEx aims to To design work clothing that has IOT embedded in it
            to securely transmit data about hazardous conditions and the miners
            physical conditions, improving safety overall in coal mines.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img
          class="d-block w-100"
          src="img/home-2.jpg"
          alt="Second slide"
        />
        <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
          <h5>Why is CoalEx important?</h5>
          <p>
            The design of the smart safety suit for the coal miner using IOT
            sensors is necessary , this suit will be equipped with the network
            of sensors such as the heartbeat sensor ,humidity sensor, gas sensor
            and the temperature sensor and the data from these sensors will be
            transmitted using wireless technology ,the alert messages are given
            through the website to the authorized person using IOT.Many
            accidents which occur in the mining industries are due to the slow
            data transmission or due to the loss of data which has to be
            transmitted, these issues can be solved by using the wireless data
            transmission technology
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img
          class="d-block w-100"
          src="img/home-5.webp"
          alt="Third slide"
        />
        <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
          <h5>How is CoalEx different?</h5>
          <p>
           CoalEx proposes to design a smart suit and a smart helmet that will be embedded with
            sensors along with an alarm system mechanism which alerts
            the user if there is any disruption in the safety.Our helmet and
            suit will be embedded with different electronics modules which helps in receiving
            and transmitting the miners data into a systematic approach.Our wireless network will ensure fast data
            transmission of small data packages through long distances.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a
      class="carousel-control-prev"
      href="#carouselExampleIndicators"
      role="button"
      data-slide="prev"
    >
      <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a
      class="carousel-control-next"
      href="#carouselExampleIndicators"
